{"tid":1793482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"po下你餐冬至飯出黎！","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:18:43.000Z","uid":234540,"like":43,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"5548ea12d8c6161bf68533dd97a36a6d5d59b298","tid":1793482,"uid":234540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"我先......商場便當<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豚肉生姜燒便當套餐配味噌湯（$42）<br />\n凍咖啡&amp;朱古力奶凍<br />\n一個人既冬至飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有飯有湯有野飲同甜品<br />\n正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHuHXuw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHuHXuw.png&h=bdfffd4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2831bacc3a8ec9b22135893431c43359ccd75cdd","tid":1793482,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"食飽飽，訓一晚，跟著去稅局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%